---
import type { CaseStudy } from '../../lib/notion';
import PaginationNav from '../PaginationNav.astro';

interface Props {
  lang: 'en' | 'zh' | 'ja';
  t: (key: any) => string;
  leadCase?: CaseStudy;
  cases: CaseStudy[];
  currentPage: number;
  totalPages: number;
}

const { lang, t, leadCase, cases, currentPage, totalPages } = Astro.props;
const paginationLabels = {
  previous: lang === 'zh' ? '上一页' : lang === 'ja' ? '前へ' : 'Previous',
  next: lang === 'zh' ? '下一页' : lang === 'ja' ? '次へ' : 'Next',
  page: lang === 'zh' ? '页码' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ページ' : 'Page',
  loadMore: lang === 'zh' ? '加载更多' : lang === 'ja' ? 'もっと見る' : 'Load more',
};
---

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-kicker">Case Desk</p>
      <h1>{t('nav.cases')}</h1>
      <p>{lang === 'zh' ? '不再按行业松散堆内容，而是用增长、自动化、产品化和一人公司路径去重组案例。' : lang === 'ja' ? '業界別の断片ではなく、成長・自動化・商品化・ひとり起業の視点でケースを再編集します。' : 'A case library organized around problems and outcomes, not loose industry buckets.'}</p>
    </div>

    {leadCase ? (
      <div class="list-shell fade-in">
        <article class="lead-entry">
          {leadCase.coverImage && (
            <div class="lead-entry-image">
              <img src={leadCase.coverImage} alt={leadCase.title} loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          )}
          <div class="lead-entry-meta">
            {(leadCase.problemType || leadCase.industry) && <span class="card-badge">{leadCase.problemType || leadCase.industry}</span>}
            {leadCase.revenue && <span class="card-badge impact-routine">{leadCase.revenue}</span>}
          </div>
          <div class="lead-entry-date">{leadCase.date}</div>
          <h2>
            <a href={`/${lang}/cases/${leadCase.slug || leadCase.id}/`}>{leadCase.title}</a>
          </h2>
          <p>{leadCase.snippet}</p>
          <div class="lead-entry-actions">
            <a href={`/${lang}/cases/${leadCase.slug || leadCase.id}/`} class="read-more">
              {t('read.more')} →
            </a>
            <span class="lead-entry-note">{lang === 'zh' ? '案例拆解' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ケース分解' : 'Case breakdown'}</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="list-aside">
          <div class="aside-card">
            <h3>{lang === 'zh' ? '一人公司能借鉴什么' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ひとり起業家が持ち帰れること' : 'What solo builders can borrow'}</h3>
            <ul class="aside-list">
              <li>{lang === 'zh' ? '哪些问题类型值得参考' : lang === 'ja' ? '参考にしやすい課題パターン' : 'Which problem patterns are worth borrowing?'}</li>
              <li>{lang === 'zh' ? '哪些变化对效率或收入有实际帮助' : lang === 'ja' ? '効率や収益に効く変化は何か' : 'Which changes clearly improved efficiency or revenue?'}</li>
              <li>{lang === 'zh' ? '哪些流程不靠团队也能复制' : lang === 'ja' ? 'チームなしでも再現しやすい流れは何か' : 'What parts can work without a larger team?'}</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="aside-card">
            <h3>{lang === 'zh' ? '怎么使用这一栏' : lang === 'ja' ? 'この欄の読み方' : 'How to use this desk'}</h3>
            <p>{lang === 'zh' ? '先按问题类型找最接近你现状的案例，再看结果和可复制的做法。这里不是为了讲励志故事，而是帮你更快找到能借用的经营动作。' : lang === 'ja' ? 'まず自分に近い課題タイプから読み始め、その後に成果と再現できる動きを見る使い方です。物語を消費するためではなく、持ち帰れる運用判断を増やすための欄です。' : 'Start with the case closest to your problem, then read for outcomes and repeatable moves. This desk is not here to tell inspiring stories; it is here to surface operating lessons you can actually reuse.'}</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    ) : null}

    <div class="card-grid editorial-list" data-paginated-list>
      {cases.map((cs, i) => (
        <article class="content-card fade-in" style={`animation-delay: ${i * 60}ms`}>
          {cs.coverImage && (
            <div class="card-cover">
              <img src={cs.coverImage} alt={cs.title} loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          )}
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-badge">{cs.problemType || cs.industry || 'Business'}</span>
            {cs.revenue && <span class="card-badge impact-routine">{cs.revenue}</span>}
          </div>
          <div class="card-date">{cs.date}</div>
          <h2>
            <a href={`/${lang}/cases/${cs.slug || cs.id}/`}>{cs.title}</a>
          </h2>
          <p class="card-snippet">{cs.snippet}</p>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <a href={`/${lang}/cases/${cs.slug || cs.id}/`} class="read-more">
              {t('read.more')} →
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
      {!leadCase && cases.length === 0 && (
        <div class="empty-state">No case studies yet.</div>
      )}
    </div>

    <PaginationNav
      basePath={`/${lang}/cases/`}
      currentPage={currentPage}
      totalPages={totalPages}
      labels={paginationLabels}
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .list-shell {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(280px, 0.46fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .lead-entry,
  .aside-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .lead-entry {
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(32, 27, 24, 0.04);
  }
  .lead-entry-image {
    margin: -8px -8px 18px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 8.6;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(177, 90, 53, 0.12), rgba(61, 100, 120, 0.14));
  }
  .lead-entry-image img,
  .card-cover img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .lead-entry-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .lead-entry-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .lead-entry h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .lead-entry p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 46rem;
  }
  .lead-entry-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .lead-entry-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .list-aside {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .aside-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.85rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .aside-card p,
  .aside-list li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .aside-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .aside-list li {
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .card-cover {
    margin: -6px -6px 18px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(177, 90, 53, 0.12), rgba(61, 100, 120, 0.14));
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .list-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
